---
import CaseStudyLayout from '../../layouts/CaseStudyLayout.astro';
import CaseStudyRow from '../../components/case-studies/CaseStudyRow.astro';
import CaseStudyImageColumn from '../../components/case-studies/CaseStudyImageColumn.astro';
import CaseStudyTextColumn from '../../components/case-studies/CaseStudyTextColumn.astro';
import CaseStudyWideImage from '../../components/case-studies/CaseStudyWideImage.astro';
import CaseStudyQuote from '../../components/case-studies/CaseStudyQuote.astro';
import { getCaseStudyBySlug } from '../../data/caseStudies';

const study = getCaseStudyBySlug('dc-marketing');

if (!study) {
  throw new Error('Missing DC Marketing case study metadata.');
}
---

<CaseStudyLayout
  slug={study.slug}
  title="DC Marketing"
  description="A case study on DC Marketing's logo design, visual identity system, and website audit work."
  summary="A refined identity package and strategic website audit created to strengthen distinction, professionalism, and consistency across the brand."
  services={study.services}
  client="DC Marketing"
  heroImage="/images/work/dc-marketing.webp"
  heroAlt="DC Marketing logo on a blue background"
>
  <CaseStudyRow>
    <CaseStudyImageColumn
      src="/images/work/DC-mockup.webp"
      alt="DC Marketing brand guidelines, logo system, and campaign mockups"
      caption=""
    />
    <CaseStudyTextColumn>
      <h2>Client Overview</h2>
      <p>
        DC Marketing is a marketing firm that supports small businesses and
        influencers in Southern California with online content curation and
        social media management. They wanted a more refined brand identity that
        could separate them from competitors and communicate professionalism,
        history, and quality with more confidence.
      </p>

      <h3>Project Goals</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Design a logo system that reflects the firm&apos;s history and expertise.</li>
        <li>Create brand guidelines for a more consistent and sophisticated identity.</li>
        <li>Conduct a website audit to uncover design, usability, and performance improvements.</li>
      </ul>
    </CaseStudyTextColumn>
  </CaseStudyRow>

  <CaseStudyWideImage
    src="/images/work/DC-Primary-Lockup-Gold.webp"
    alt="DC Marketing primary logo lockup"
    caption=""
  />

  <CaseStudyRow>
    <CaseStudyTextColumn>
      <h2>Challenges</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Creating a logo that felt established, refined, and distinct.</li>
        <li>Developing guidelines that could unify the brand across every touchpoint.</li>
        <li>Performing a thorough website audit that produced actionable next steps.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Solutions</h3>
      <p><strong>Branding</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Developed a logo inspired by classic sports-mark references while keeping the final identity polished and professional.</li>
        <li>Built supporting brand guidelines covering color, typography, and usage rules for consistency.</li>
      </ul>
      <p><strong>Website Audit</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Reviewed design, performance, usability, and SEO to identify priority improvements.</li>
        <li>Delivered recommendations around speed, navigation, and content effectiveness.</li>
      </ul>
    </CaseStudyTextColumn>
    <CaseStudyImageColumn
      src="/images/work/DC-Brand-Guide.png"
      alt="DC Marketing single page brand guide"
      caption=""
    />
  </CaseStudyRow>

  <CaseStudyQuote author="DC Marketing engagement">
    The goal was to create a brand package that felt more established and
    differentiated while giving the team a clearer foundation for consistent
    digital presentation.
  </CaseStudyQuote>

  <CaseStudyRow>
    <CaseStudyImageColumn
      src="/images/work/DC-mockup3.png"
      alt="DC Marketing visual identity presentation and collateral mockups"
      caption=""
    />
    <CaseStudyTextColumn>
      <h2>Results</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>The new logo and identity package gave DC Marketing a more polished and differentiated brand presence.</li>
        <li>The website audit produced practical improvements to strengthen performance and usability.</li>
        <li>The completed guidelines created a more cohesive visual system across future materials.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Summary</h3>
      <p>
        This project shows RedTail&apos;s ability to deliver strategic identity work
        alongside actionable website guidance. The result is a stronger brand
        foundation and a clearer path toward a more effective online presence.
      </p>
    </CaseStudyTextColumn>
  </CaseStudyRow>
</CaseStudyLayout>
